19#include "GridSampler.h"
20
21namespace ZXing {
22
23DetectorResult SampleGrid(const BitMatrix& image, int width, int height, const PerspectiveTransform& transform)
24{
25 auto project = [&](PointI p) { return PointI(transform(p + PointF(0.5, 0.5))); };
26 auto isInside = [&](PointI p) {
27 p = project(p);
28 return 0 <= p.x && p.x < image.width() && 0 <= p.y && p.y < image.height();
29 };
30
31 if (width <= 0 || height <= 0 || !transform.isValid() || !isInside({0, 0}) || !isInside({width - 1, 0}) ||
32 !isInside({width - 1, height - 1}) || !isInside({0, height - 1}))
33 return {};
34
35 BitMatrix res(width, height);
36 for (int y = 0; y < height; ++y)
37 for (int x = 0; x < width; ++x) {
38 auto p = project({x, y});
39 if (image.get(p.x, p.y))
40 res.set(x, y);
41 }
42 auto projectCorner = [&](PointI p) { return PointI(transform(PointF(p)) + PointF(0.5, 0.5)); };
43 return {
44 std::move(res),
45 {projectCorner({0, 0}), projectCorner({width, 0}), projectCorner({width, height}), projectCorner({0, height})}};
46}
47
48} // ZXing
